  "texts": [
    "This investigation serves as a critical step in determining whether the feedback imparted by peers and AI holds the necessary caliber to enhance the craft of essay writing.",
    "The ramifications of addressing this query are noteworthy.",
    "Firstly, it stands to significantly alleviate the workload carried by teachers in the process of essay evaluation.",
    "By ascertaining the viability of feedback from peers and AI, teachers can potentially reduce the time and effort expended in reviewing essays.",
    "Furthermore, this study has the potential to advance the quality of essay compositions."
  ]
}